properties.DESC: New Hope Road is a two-lane roadway that connects the Southwest portion of Cherokee County over to Red Top Mountain State Park and portion of Lake Alatoona.
properties.JUST: This roadway is frequently used by recreational vehicles and vehicles with boat trailers accessing the many campgrounds and lake access points in the area.
